{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T17:06:01.121Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Sending PDFs"},{"type":"text","text":" in Claude's PDF Support is the process of uploading PDF documents to enable deep analysis, text extraction, chart interpretation, and visual content understanding. When you send a PDF, Claude processes it as both text and images for comprehensive understanding."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What it is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sending PDFs means attaching PDF documents to your Claude conversation so the AI can "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"parse, analyze, and reason over the entire document"},{"type":"text","text":" rather than just surface-level summarization."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why it matters"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Traditional PDF Reading"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude PDF Analysis"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Manual page-by-page reading"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Ingests entire document"},{"type":"text","text":" into context"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":